{"tid":1930672,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普：經濟將迅速復元　財長未來兩周將向國民發支票    百萬富翁將不會受惠","createTime":"2020-03-17T17:02:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-18T01:25:04.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e0f1ca839844d84bf974d4afb05c0204d94357a5","tid":1930672,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:02:42.000Z","msg":"美國至今有超過80人死於新型冠狀病毒，大部分在華盛頓州。<br />\n<br />\n總統特朗普表示，有關病毒的檢測工作正在有序進行，他昨日表示，美國的經濟可能會衰退，他今日補充，相信美國經濟會迅速復元。<br />\n<br />\n白宮據報正擬定一份規模達8500億美元的振興經濟方案。<br />\n<br />\n財長努欽表示，總統特朗普向他作出指示，希望在未來兩星期，向國民寄出支票，透過經濟補助民眾打擊疫情。努欽未有交代實際金額，但表示金額很大，百萬富翁將不會受惠。<br />\n<br />\n努欽又表示，當局正致力維持金融市場維持開放，但可能減少交易時間，他又形容，現時新型肺炎對航空業的打擊，較九一一時更加嚴重，當局將推出措施，協助業界。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515130-20200318.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515130-20200318.htm&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=b1bee3a4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515130-20200318.htm&h=ba501cff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515130-20200318.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d29e9b16af52548892927937426ac2bd326b810b","tid":1930672,"uid":4258,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:04:12.000Z","msg":"快啲死晒快啲復原，bojo 無做錯到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b07f000f115b2a02c17c7735b05c7ebeaedba4","tid":1930672,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:05:08.000Z","msg":"兩星期<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf187435af8fdc4aed7ab6ca0f12dfcb512db858","tid":1930672,"uid":8014,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-17T17:05:27.000Z","m